<mvc:View controllerName="journeyPlanner.JourneyPlanner.controller.HistoricalJourneyPlanner" 
    xmlns="sap.m" 
    xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
    xmlns:semantic="sap.m.semantic"
    xmlns:c="http://schemas.sap.com/sapui5/extension/sap.ui.core.CustomData/1"
	xmlns:core="sap.ui.core"
	xmlns:viz="sap.viz.ui5.controls" 
	xmlns:viz.data="sap.viz.ui5.data"
	xmlns:viz.feeds="sap.viz.ui5.controls.common.feeds">
	<semantic:FullscreenPage title="Historical Journey Planner" 
							 navButtonPress="onHistoricalJourneyPlannerNavBack" 
							 showNavButton="true" 
							 busy="{HistoricalJourneyPlanner>/FullScreenPageBusy}">
		<semantic:content>
			<VBox class="sapUiSmallMarginBeginEnd 
						 sapUiSmallMarginTopBottom" 
				  width="100%">
				<HBox>
					<VBox width="20%">
						<ComboBox id="idStationDropDown" 
								  class="smartJourneyPlannerStationDropDowns"
								  items="{path: 'HistoricalJourneyPlanner>/MetroStations', 
										  sorter: {path: 'Station_Name'}}"
								  selectedKey="{HistoricalJourneyPlanner>/NewStationClientCopy/Station}" 
								  width="100%"
								  placeholder="Station" 
								  required="true" 
								  c:dropdown="Station"
								  change="onDropDownSelectionChange">
							<core:Item key="{HistoricalJourneyPlanner>Station_Name}" 
									   text="{HistoricalJourneyPlanner>Station_Name}" />
						</ComboBox>
					</VBox>
					<VBox width="20%">
						<ComboBox id="idDayDropDown" 
								  class="smartJourneyPlannerStationDropDowns sapUiTinyMarginBegin"
								  items="{HistoricalJourneyPlanner>/Days}"
								  selectedKey="{HistoricalJourneyPlanner>/NewStationClientCopy/Day}" 
								  width="100%"
								  placeholder="Day" 
								  required="true" 
								  c:dropdown="Day"
								  change="onDropDownSelectionChange">
							<core:Item key="{HistoricalJourneyPlanner>Day_Text}" 
									   text="{HistoricalJourneyPlanner>Day_Text}" />
						</ComboBox>
					</VBox>
					<Button text="Submit" 
							type="Emphasized" 
							class="sapUiSmallMarginBegin"
							press="onPressSubmitButton">
					</Button>
				</HBox>
				<VBox height="6rem" 
					  class="sapUiSmallMarginTopBottom 
							 sapUiMediumMarginEnd 
							 smartJourneyPlannerJourneyStation"
					  visible="{HistoricalJourneyPlanner>/EmptyVBoxVisiblity}">
					<Text text="Select a valid Station and Day" 
						  class="sapUiMediumMarginTop 
								 sapUiMediumMarginEnd 
								 smartJourneyPlannerJourneyEmptyVBox">
					</Text>
				</VBox>
				<VBox visible="{= !${HistoricalJourneyPlanner>/EmptyVBoxVisiblity}}">
					<viz:VizFrame id="idCrowdVizFrame"
							      uiConfig="{applicationSet:'fiori'}" 
							      height='500px' 
							      width="100%" 
							      vizType='line'>
						<viz:dataset>
							<viz.data:FlattenedDataset data="{HistoricalJourneyPlanner>/CrowdData}">
								<viz.data:dimensions>
									<viz.data:DimensionDefinition name="Time" 
																  value="{path:'HistoricalJourneyPlanner>time', 
																		  type:'sap.ui.model.odata.type.Time'}"/>
								</viz.data:dimensions>
								<viz.data:measures>
									<viz.data:MeasureDefinition name="Crowd" 
																value="{HistoricalJourneyPlanner>crowd1}"/>
									<viz.data:MeasureDefinition name="Capacity" 
																value="{HistoricalJourneyPlanner>capacity}"/>
								</viz.data:measures>
							</viz.data:FlattenedDataset>
						</viz:dataset>
						<viz:feeds>
							<viz.feeds:FeedItem id="valueAxisFeed" 
												uid="valueAxis" 
												type="Measure" 
												values="Crowd"/>
						    <viz.feeds:FeedItem id="valueAxisFeed1" 
						    					uid="valueAxis" 
						    					type="Measure" 
						    					values="Capacity"/>
							<viz.feeds:FeedItem id="categoryAxisFeed" 
												uid="categoryAxis" 
												type="Dimension" 
												values="Time"/>
						</viz:feeds>
					</viz:VizFrame>
				</VBox>
			</VBox>
		</semantic:content>
	</semantic:FullscreenPage>
</mvc:View>